Package: ePiE
Type: Package
Title: ePiE model R-package
Version: 1.25
Date: 2025-08-29
Author: Selwyn Hoeks, Rik Oldenkamp
Maintainer: Selwyn Hoeks <selwyn.hoeks@ru.nl>
Description: ePiE is a spatially explicit model that estimates concentrations of active pharmaceutical ingredients (APIs) in surface waters across Europe. This repository contains the R package of the ePiE model alongside all the required input parameters, such as the parameterized European river catchment and discharge data.
